","tid":1984601,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43c750dddc82ec075907c305a0505879c828469a","tid":1984601,"uid":189430,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"淨係睇完第一名係邊個都知個排名唔知用乜野做標準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"The Times Higher Education Impact Rankings are the only global performance tables that assess universities against the United Nations&rsquo; Sustainable Development Goals. We use carefully calibrated indicators to provide comprehensive and balanced comparisons across three broad areas: research, outreach, and stewardship.<br />\n<br />\nThis first edition includes more than 450 universities from 76 countries.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.timeshighereducation.com/rankings/impact/2019/overall#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/undefined\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeshighereducation.com%2Frankings%2Fimpact%2F2019%2Foverall%23%21%2Fpage%2F0%2Flength%2F25%2Fsort_by%2Frank%2Fsort_order%2Fasc%2Fcols%2Fundefined&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=69e875ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.timeshighereducation.com/rankings/impact/2019/overall#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/undefined</a>"},{"pid":"323df396f5a75ad68a93d4cdd7f0d7dd7c77ab15","tid":1984601,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d58718bf84d49162f511c8be094592f5cbeea422","tid":1984601,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=582fdd31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】英國《泰晤士報高等教育特刊》(THE)今(22日)公布2020年大學影響力排名，本港多間大學排名下跌。其中去年躋身綜合排名第10位的香港大學今年跌至第41位，但仍是本港唯一一間排名前100位的大學，至於去年第60名的香港浸會大學亦跌至100位後。不過，在多個細項中，港大在「和平、正義及強大機構」一項勇奪亞軍，而嶺南大學亦在「優質教育」一項名列世界第2位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該排名是按聯合國17個可持續發展目標（SDG）作衡量標準，以比較全球大學在社會影響力的表現，今年有89個國家、逾850間大學參與評估，較去年增加301間。本港院校僅港大成功躋身前百位，排行第41，較去年下跌31位，該校在「和平、正義及強大機構」方面仍然排行全球第2位，該排名以參與政府顧問工作及學術自由政策等方面表現為依據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學則在「優質教育」方面排行世界第2位，該校稱其綜合排名約為第101至200位，但在「無貧窮」及「體面工作和經濟增長」方面分別獲第48位及第71位。該校校長鄭國漢稱對排名感歡迎，證明嶺大在優質教育的承諾和貢獻獲國際學術界認可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於全球表現方面，綜合排名第一位由新西蘭的奧克蘭大學蟬聯冠軍，澳洲學府則包辦第2至第4名，分別為悉尼大學、西悉尼大學及拉籌伯大學。另外，內地同濟大學、台灣成功大學及彰化師範大學則分別排名第13、38及66位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港大回應指，該排名有別於其他的學術排名，影響力排名着眼於大學對社會和經濟所發揮的影響力，以及對政府、商業社會以及廣大群眾帶來的正面意義。該校指在大部分細項分數都有所提高，尤其有一分項排名全球第2。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E5%A0%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%B1%E7%AC%AC10%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B341%E4%BD%8D-110937975.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%2590%258D-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B1%25E7%25AC%25AC10%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2587%25B341%25E4%25BD%258D-110937975.html&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=b5704488\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E5%A0%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%B1%E7%AC%AC10%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B341%E4%BD%8D-110937975.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"牛劍哈麻：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f2f291bc8f8f6f7c9c4726681e5f5591df54a5","tid":1984601,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8d54e50827f909c0f24e776691ebc7c1ff043153","tid":1984601,"uid":50176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"嶺南算唔算俾羅37一個拉高<img src